data.description: PRICE IMPROVED! This is one of the largest of the floorplans in Spencer Crossing at almost 2000 sq ft. Numerous upgrades like NEW kitchen cupboards, granite counters, SS appliances and NEW flooring in most rooms. (2022-2023) NEWER roof and HVAC (2019) and updated plumbing.  Vaulted ceilings, GIGANTIC great room, extra flex room for formal dining, game room or office,. Fenced yard with raised garden beds. Clay county schools and mere minutes to groceries, Oakleaf Town Center, NAS JAX, restaurants and all major commuter routes. Quiet well-established neighborhood with mature trees AND NO CDD/LOW ANNUAL HOA! Even comes with a Home Warranty for your peace of mind!
